nodes.text: Joventusek was a city that was located on the planet of Caarimon. Its name was the Caarimala word for "gateway" and all starships that arrived on Caarimon had to pass through the city. Like all Caarimon cities, it floated just above the surface of the planet and was powered by the byproducts of Buehl grass
The Metatheran Cartel had some offices in Joventusek, which they named Cartel Central.
